# HACA Project Licensing

The Host-Agnostic Cognitive Architecture (HACA) project uses different licenses for the specification and the reference implementation.

## 1. Specification License

All documentation and specification files located in the `/HACA` directory are licensed under the **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)**.

You are free to:
- **Share** — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format.
- **Adapt** — remix, transform, and build upon the material for any purpose, even commercially.

Under the following terms:
- **Attribution** — You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.

Full license text: [https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)

